<div class="ui large message">
  <h1 class="ui huge center aligned header">FAQ</h1>
  <div class="ui divided items">
    <div class="link item">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="header">How does this work?</p>
        <div class="description">
          Sign up and take a brief diagnostic. We’ll send you a book when the next class starts.  Follow the weekly reading schedule and answer reading questions online. A native English-speaking teacher will review your responses and give you feedback[a].
          We’ll send you another book the following month and the fun starts again!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="link item">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="header">Can I buy this subscription for my child or a friend?</p>
        <div class="description">
          Yes.  If you purchase a subscription for someone else, you can send them an invite to create their own account.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="link item">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="header">Can I pause my subscription?</p>
        <div class="description">
          Yes. With a one-year subscription, you can pause your subscription for one month.

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="link item">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="header">What will I read? </p>
        <div class="description">
          Award-winning books by a variety of authors. The books have been carefully selected to expose the student to a wide range of subjects, styles, content, etc…Our proprietary algorithms ensure that the content is appropriate for your child's level. Our teachers will ensure that they find it engaging.

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ui divider"></div>
  <h2 class="ui center aligned header">
    <%= link_to raw("Sign Up &raquo;"), new_user_registration_path, :class => "ui blue button huge" %>
    <%= link_to raw("Log In &raquo;"), new_user_session_path, :class => "ui blue button huge" %>
  </h2>
</div>
